OL,3,CArmed thief tracked down from
OL,4,Cdistinctive hand tattoo
OL,6,FAn armed thief's distinctive hand
OL,7,Ftattoo has helped officers prove he
OL,8,Fwas responsible for robbing a
OL,9,FTunbridge Wells shop at knifepoint.
OL,11,FArchie Pattullo was sentenced to three
OL,12,Fyears and nine months' in jail after
OL,13,Fhe threatened a shopkeeper in the High
OL,14,FBrooms area.
OL,16,FAt around 10.30pm on 30 June 2025,
OL,17,FPattullo entered a convenience store
OL,18,Fwearing a face covering.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
