PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773083489
OL,3,CArmed thief tracked down from
OL,4,Cdistinctive hand tattoo
OL,6,FHe cornered a member of staff behind
OL,7,Fthe till while brandishing a knife,
OL,8,Faggressively demanded money, and left
OL,9,Fwith approximately #1,800 in cash.
OL,11,FOfficers attended the scene and
OL,12,Frecovered CCTV, with a constable
OL,13,Freviewing the footage recognising the
OL,14,Fsuspect's hand tattoo.
OL,16,FTeams attempted to arrest him at his
OL,17,Fhome address in Chestnut Close, but
OL,18,FPattullo had fled.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
