PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773083489
OL,3,CArmed thief tracked down from
OL,4,Cdistinctive hand tattoo
OL,6,FWhile tracking him down, officers
OL,7,Fseized clothing from the bin of a
OL,8,Fneighbouring property which matched
OL,9,Fthe hoodie, T shirt, and trainers he
OL,10,Fwas wearing when caught on camera.
OL,12,FPattullo was later arrested in
OL,13,FBrighton on 4 July and a review of his
OL,14,Fseized mobile phone revealed messages
OL,15,Fin which he bragged to a friend about
OL,16,Fhaving a large quantity of cash from
OL,17,F'a job'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
