CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773083489
OL,3,CArmed thief tracked down from
OL,4,Cdistinctive hand tattoo
OL,6,FHe was charged the following day with
OL,7,Frobbery and possession of a bladed
OL,8,Farticle. The 26 year old pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to the offences and was
OL,10,Fsentenced at Maidstone Crown Court on
OL,11,F25 February 2026.
OL,13,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,14,FConstable Celia King, said: "Pattullo
OL,15,Fthreatened his victim causing him
OL,16,Fextreme distress, all for the sake of
OL,17,Flining his pockets.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
