FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773083489
OL,3,CArmed thief tracked down from
OL,4,Cdistinctive hand tattoo
OL,6,F"The investigating team were able to
OL,7,Fdraw upon their knowledge of the area
OL,8,Fand those persons of interest and by
OL,9,Fidentifying Pattullo's distinctive
OL,10,Fhand tattoo were quickly able to
OL,11,Fidentify him as the suspect.
OL,13,F"Despite fleeing to another town in
OL,14,Fanother county, he was tracked down by
OL,15,FKent Police and brought to justice,
OL,16,Fwhich shows how relentless we are when
OL,17,Fit comes to pursuing criminals."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
